 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-title",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# 🚀 Qwen2.5-32B + Open WebUI + Cloudflare Tunnel\n",
    "\n",
    "**使用前检查：**\n",
    "- Notebook Settings → Accelerator → **GPU T4 x2**\n",
    "- Notebook Settings → Internet → **已开启**\n",
    "\n",
    "**运行方法：** 按顺序运行每个 Cell，最后一个 Cell 会输出公网访问地址。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-step1-title",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Step 1：检查 GPU 状态"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-check-gpu",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import subprocess\n",
    "result = subprocess.run(['nvidia-smi'], capture_output=True, text=True)\n",
    "print(result.stdout)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 确认显存总量（T4x2应显示约30GB）\n",
    "import torch\n",
    "if torch.cuda.is_available():\n",
    "    for i in range(torch.cuda.device_count()):\n",
    "        props = torch.cuda.get_device_properties(i)\n",
    "        print(f\"GPU {i}: {props.name}, 显存: {props.total_memory / 1024**3:.1f} GB\")\n",
    "else:\n",
    "    print('❌ 未检测到GPU，请在Notebook Settings中开启 T4 x2')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-step2-title",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Step 2：安装依赖"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-install",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "%%bash\n",
    "pip install -q huggingface_hub hf_transfer\n",
    "\n",
    "# 安装 llama-cpp-python（支持双GPU）\n",
    "CMAKE_ARGS=\"-DGGML_CUDA=on -DGGML_CUDA_FORCE_MMQ=ON\" \\\n",
    "FORCE_CMAKE=1 \\\n",
    "pip install -q llama-cpp-python \\\n",
    "    --extra-index-url https://abetlen.github.io/llama-cpp-python/whl/cu124\n",
    "\n",
    "# 安装 Open WebUI\n",
    "pip install -q open-webui\n",
    "\n",
    "# 安装 Cloudflare Tunnel\n",
    "wget -q https://github.com/cloudflare/cloudflared/releases/latest/download/cloudflared-linux-amd64 \\\n",
    "    -O /usr/local/bin/cloudflared\n",
    "chmod +x /usr/local/bin/cloudflared\n",
    "\n",
    "echo \"✅ 所有依赖安装完成\""
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-step3-title",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Step 3：下载模型\n",
    "\n",
    "> 首次运行需要下载约 **20GB**，大约需要 15-25 分钟。  \n",
    "> 下载完成后建议保存为 Kaggle Dataset，之后可以秒速加载（见文档说明）。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-download-model",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import os\n",
    "from huggingface_hub import hf_hub_download\n",
    "\n",
    "os.environ[\"HF_HUB_ENABLE_HF_TRANSFER\"] = \"1\"\n",
    "\n",
    "MODEL_DIR = \"/kaggle/working/models\"\n",
    "os.makedirs(MODEL_DIR, exist_ok=True)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 使用 ModelScope 镜像加速下载（国内友好）\n",
    "# 模型：Qwen2.5-32B-Instruct Q4_K_M 量化版\n",
    "MODEL_REPO = \"Qwen/Qwen2.5-32B-Instruct-GGUF\"\n",
    "MODEL_FILE = \"qwen2.5-32b-instruct-q4_k_m.gguf\"\n",
    "MODEL_PATH = os.path.join(MODEL_DIR, MODEL_FILE)\n",
    "\n",
    "if os.path.exists(MODEL_PATH):\n",
    "    size_gb = os.path.getsize(MODEL_PATH) / 1024**3\n",
    "    print(f\"✅ 模型已存在：{size_gb:.1f} GB，跳过下载\")\n",
    "else:\n",
    "    print(f\"⬇️ 开始下载 {MODEL_FILE}...\")\n",
    "    print(\"预计大小：约 20GB，请耐心等待...\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    hf_hub_download(\n",
    "        repo_id=MODEL_REPO,\n",
    "        filename=MODEL_FILE,\n",
    "        local_dir=MODEL_DIR,\n",
    "        local_dir_use_symlinks=False,\n",
    "    )\n",
    "    print(f\"✅ 下载完成：{MODEL_PATH}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"\\n模型路径：{MODEL_PATH}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-step4-title",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Step 4：启动 llama.cpp 推理服务器\n",
    "\n",
    "将模型分布在两张 T4 GPU 上运行，上下文长度设为 **32K tokens**。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-start-llama",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import subprocess, time, requests\n",
    "\n",
    "LLAMA_PORT = 8080\n",
    "\n",
    "llama_cmd = [\n",
    "    \"python\", \"-m\", \"llama_cpp.server\",\n",
    "    \"--model\", MODEL_PATH,\n",
    "    \"--host\", \"0.0.0.0\",\n",
    "    \"--port\", str(LLAMA_PORT),\n",
    "    \"--n_gpu_layers\", \"99\",       # 全部层放GPU\n",
    "    \"--n_ctx\", \"32768\",            # 32K 上下文\n",
    "    \"--n_batch\", \"512\",\n",
    "    \"--tensor_split\", \"1,1\",       # 平均分配到两张GPU\n",
    "    \"--chat_format\", \"chatml\",\n",
    "    \"--verbose\", \"false\",\n",
    "]\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"🚀 正在启动 llama.cpp 服务器...\")\n",
    "llama_proc = subprocess.Popen(\n",
    "    llama_cmd,\n",
    "    stdout=subprocess.PIPE,\n",
    "    stderr=subprocess.STDOUT,\n",
    "    text=True\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 等待服务器就绪（最多等90秒）\n",
    "print(\"等待模型加载完成（约30-60秒）...\")\n",
    "for i in range(90):\n",
    "    time.sleep(2)\n",
    "    try:\n",
    "        r = requests.get(f\"http://localhost:{LLAMA_PORT}/v1/models\", timeout=3)\n",
    "        if r.status_code == 200:\n",
    "            print(f\"\\n✅ llama.cpp 服务器已启动！端口：{LLAMA_PORT}\")\n",
    "            print(f\"模型信息：{r.json()}\")\n",
    "            break\n",
    "    except:\n",
    "        print(f\"  加载中... {(i+1)*2}s\", end=\"\\r\")\n",
    "else:\n",
    "    print(\"\\n❌ 启动超时，查看错误输出：\")\n",
    "    out, _ = llama_proc.communicate(timeout=5)\n",
    "    print(out[-3000:])"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-step5-title",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Step 5：启动 Open WebUI\n",
    "\n",
    "Open WebUI 提供类 ChatGPT 的对话界面，连接本地 llama.cpp 服务。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-start-webui",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import subprocess, time, requests, os\n",
    "\n",
    "WEBUI_PORT = 3000\n",
    "\n",
    "env = os.environ.copy()\n",
    "env.update({\n",
    "    \"OLLAMA_BASE_URL\": \"\",                                  # 不使用Ollama\n",
    "    \"OPENAI_API_BASE_URL\": f\"http://localhost:8080/v1\",     # 连接llama.cpp\n",
    "    \"OPENAI_API_KEY\": \"sk-no-key\",\n",
    "    \"WEBUI_AUTH\": \"False\",                                   # 关闭登录（方便使用）\n",
    "    \"PORT\": str(WEBUI_PORT),\n",
    "    \"HOST\": \"0.0.0.0\",\n",
    "})\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"🌐 正在启动 Open WebUI...\")\n",
    "webui_proc = subprocess.Popen(\n",
    "    [\"open-webui\", \"serve\"],\n",
    "    env=env,\n",
    "    stdout=subprocess.PIPE,\n",
    "    stderr=subprocess.STDOUT,\n",
    "    text=True\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 等待WebUI就绪\n",
    "for i in range(60):\n",
    "    time.sleep(2)\n",
    "    try:\n",
    "        r = requests.get(f\"http://localhost:{WEBUI_PORT}\", timeout=3)\n",
    "        if r.status_code == 200:\n",
    "            print(f\"✅ Open WebUI 已启动！端口：{WEBUI_PORT}\")\n",
    "            break\n",
    "    except:\n",
    "        print(f\"  启动中... {(i+1)*2}s\", end=\"\\r\")\n",
    "else:\n",
    "    print(\"\\n❌ WebUI启动超时，查看输出：\")\n",
    "    print(webui_proc.stdout.read(3000))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-step6-title",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Step 6：Cloudflare Tunnel 暴露公网地址\n",
    "\n",
    "运行后会输出一个 `https://xxxx.trycloudflare.com` 地址，手机浏览器直接打开即可。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-cloudflare",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import subprocess, threading, time, re\n",
    "\n",
    "cf_url = None\n",
    "url_found = threading.Event()\n",
    "\n",
    "def read_cf_output(proc):\n",
    "    global cf_url\n",
    "    for line in proc.stderr:\n",
    "        # 提取 trycloudflare.com 地址\n",
    "        match = re.search(r'https://[\\w-]+\\.trycloudflare\\.com', line)\n",
    "        if match:\n",
    "            cf_url = match.group(0)\n",
    "            url_found.set()\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"🌍 正在建立 Cloudflare Tunnel...\")\n",
    "cf_proc = subprocess.Popen(\n",
    "    [\"cloudflared\", \"tunnel\", \"--url\", f\"http://localhost:3000\"],\n",
    "    stdout=subprocess.PIPE,\n",
    "    stderr=subprocess.PIPE,\n",
    "    text=True\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "t = threading.Thread(target=read_cf_output, args=(cf_proc,), daemon=True)\n",
    "t.start()\n",
    "\n",
    "# 等待URL出现\n",
    "if url_found.wait(timeout=30):\n",
    "    print(\"\\n\" + \"=\"*55)\n",
    "    print(\"✅ 隧道建立成功！\")\n",
    "    print(f\"\\n📱 手机浏览器访问：\")\n",
    "    print(f\"\\n   👉 {cf_url}\")\n",
    "    print(\"\\n\" + \"=\"*55)\n",
    "    print(\"⚠️  注意：\")\n",
    "    print(\"  · 保持此 Notebook 运行，关闭即断开\")\n",
    "    print(\"  · 每次重启地址会变化\")\n",
    "    print(\"  · 每周GPU配额30小时，用完自动停止\")\n",
    "else:\n",
    "    print(\"❌ 获取地址超时，查看输出：\")\n",
    "    print(cf_proc.stderr.read(2000))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-novel-prompt",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 附：长篇小说创作专用 System Prompt\n",
    "\n",
    "在 Open WebUI 中：**左下角头像 → Settings → System Prompt**，粘贴以下内容：\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "```\n",
    "你是一位专业的中文小说作家，擅长创作情节紧凑、人物立体的长篇小说。\n",
    "\n",
    "写作规则：\n",
    "1. 严格保持人物性格、外貌、关系的前后一致性\n",
    "2. 每次续写前先回顾已有的关键信息（人物、地点、未解决的冲突）\n",
    "3. 每章结尾设置钩子，吸引读者继续阅读\n",
    "4. 对话要符合人物身份和性格，避免所有人说话风格相同\n",
    "5. 场景描写要有代入感，调动视觉、听觉、触觉等感官\n",
    "6. 避免重复用词和套路化表达\n",
    "7. 每次生成约1500-2000字，保持节奏稳定\n",
    "\n",
    "收到写作指令后直接开始写作，不需要解释或确认。\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "### RAG 使用方法（上传资料文档）\n",
    "\n",
    "在 Open WebUI 对话框中点击 📎 图标，直接上传你的 txt 资料文件，\n",
    "Open WebUI 会自动切片并检索相关内容，配合上方 System Prompt 效果最佳。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-tips",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 常见问题\n",
    "\n",
    "**Q: 显存不够报错？**  \n",
    "A: 将 Step 4 中 `n_ctx` 改为 `16384`（16K），或改用 Q3_K_M 量化版本。\n",
    "\n",
    "**Q: 下载太慢？**  \n",
    "A: 在 Step 3 开头加入：\n",
    "```python\n",
    "os.environ[\"HF_ENDPOINT\"] = \"https://hf-mirror.com\"  # 使用镜像\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "**Q: 如何保存模型避免每次重下？**  \n",
    "A: 下载完成后，在 Kaggle 右侧面板点击 **「+ Add Data」→「New Dataset」**，\n",
    "把 `/kaggle/working/models/` 目录保存为私有 Dataset。\n",
    "之后新建 Notebook 时挂载该 Dataset，模型路径改为 `/kaggle/input/你的dataset名/qwen2.5-32b-instruct-q4_k_m.gguf`。\n",
    "\n",
    "**Q: Cloudflare 地址打开显示警告页面？**  \n",
    "A: 正常现象，点击「Click to proceed」即可进入。"
   ]
  }
 ]
